General.Name: Q Interline AS
General.Description: Q-Interline A/S develops and manufactures analytical solutions and measuring equipment for process and product quality optimization. The company offers quant analyser, InSight Pro, DairyQuant Go, AnalyticTrust, proficiency test, InSightView, and InfraQuant solutions. It serves dairy, agriculture, food and ingredients, chemical, and pharmaceutical industries. The company was incorporated in 1996 and is based in Tølløse, Denmark.
